title: Anyone notice the lack of knee brace on Palmer against the Lions?
text: Posts: 2,541 Anyone notice the lack of knee brace on Palmer against the Lions? Not sure if this was posted in another thread, but apparently Palmer forgot to pack his knee brace for the road trip and had to play the Lions without it. I'm curious if that has anything to do with the first couple throws for CP on Sunday.
